  <prompt>
    Author the synthesis system prompt covering 7 baseline diagnostic dimensions per FR-12 (composite grade explanation; trend; themes from Notes; inflection-point detection; critical assessments cited as anchors; forward-looking risk; honest evidence-gap acknowledgment). Persist to `sprk_analysisaction.sprk_systemprompt` via the `jps-action-create` skill. Use exact KPI Performance Area names per FR-13 (Guideline Compliance, Budget Compliance, Outcomes Achievement). Apply Spaarke Canonical Prompt Construction Pattern (audit §2.7).
  </prompt>

  <role>JPS prompt engineer + legal-domain SME proxy.</role>

  <goal>
    One `sprk_analysisaction` row exists in dev Dataverse carrying the matter-health synthesis prompt. Prompt yields valid 7-dimension narrative when invoked against a sample Matter.
  </goal>

  <inputs>
    <file purpose="spec">projects/ai-spaarke-insights-engine-widgets-r1/spec.md (FR-12, FR-13)</file>
    <file purpose="design">projects/ai-spaarke-insights-engine-widgets-r1/design.md (§4.2 dimensions)</file>
    <file purpose="canonical-pattern">projects/bff-ai-architecture-audit-r1/notes/canonical-architecture-decisions.md §2.7</file>
    <file purpose="reference-prompt">existing predict-matter-cost synthesis prompt (in sprk_analysisaction)</file>
  </inputs>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="audit-DR-007 / canonical-architecture-decisions.md §2.7">Prompt lives in sprk_analysisaction.sprk_systemprompt, NOT in .txt or /Prompts/ folder (audit-codified pattern; NOT ADR-014 — citation corrected 2026-06-10)</constraint>
    <constraint source="audit-§2.7">Apply Canonical Prompt Construction Pattern</constraint>
    <constraint source="Q-U1">No `@v1`/`@vN` in action code</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec-FR-13">Exact KPI names: Guideline Compliance / Budget Compliance / Outcomes Achievement</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <topic>jps action create, system prompt, sprk_analysisaction, canonical prompt pattern</topic>
    <files>
      <file>.claude/skills/jps-action-create/SKILL.md</file>
      <file>docs/guides/JPS-AUTHORING-GUIDE.md</file>
      <file>docs/architecture/playbook-architecture.md</file>
      <file>projects/bff-ai-architecture-audit-r1/notes/canonical-architecture-decisions.md</file>
      <file>projects/ai-spaarke-insights-engine-widgets-r1/design.md</file>
      <file>projects/ai-spaarke-insights-engine-widgets-r1/spec.md</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step order="1" name="Invoke jps-action-create skill">Per its workflow</step>
    <step order="2" name="Compose 7-dimension prompt">Each dimension addressed; cite KPI names exactly</step>
    <step order="3" name="Apply Canonical Prompt Construction Pattern">Structure: role, task, constraints, context</step>
    <step order="4" name="Define output schema">Markdown body + citations array shape</step>
    <step order="5" name="Persist to sprk_analysisaction">New action row; action code = `matter-health-synthesis` (no @v suffix)</step>
    <step order="6" name="Test invocation against sample data">Verify 7 dimensions appear in output</step>
  </steps>

  <outputs>
    <output type="dataverse-data">One sprk_analysisaction row with synthesis prompt</output>
    <output type="notes">projects/ai-spaarke-insights-engine-widgets-r1/notes/handoffs/matter-health-prompt-design.md</output>
  </outputs>

  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">sprk_analysisaction row exists with action code `matter-health-synthesis` (no @v suffix)</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Test invocation produces output covering all 7 dimensions</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Output uses exact KPI Performance Area names per FR-13</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">No new .txt prompt file created (audit-DR-007 / canonical-architecture-decisions.md §2.7)</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>

  <notes>
    Completed 2026-06-10. sprk_analysisaction row id 5981632e-4165-f111-ab0c-7ced8ddc4cc6 (sprk_actioncode=matter-health-synthesis, executor action type=60 Agent Service). All 4 acceptance criteria PASS. 7 DIMENSION constraints encoded + dedicated KPI NAMING constraint forbidding abbreviation/synonym; FR-13 names appear 15/9/8 times. Zero @vN vernacular (Q-U1 ban respected). Two embedded examples cover full diagnostic (D1-D6 narrative) + Decline path (D7 evidence-gap). No .txt file created — canonical surface is sprk_systemprompt per audit DR-007 / canonical-architecture-decisions.md §2.7. Live LLM invocation deferred to playbook UAT task downstream (matter-health-single playbook does not exist yet). Handoff: notes/handoffs/matter-health-prompt-design.md.
  </notes>
</task>
